== 發行 ==
2014年2月13日，電影的發行權從[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]改由[[哥倫比亞影業|哥倫比亞影業]]負責，並宣布於2015年7月31日上映<ref>{{cite web |last=Fleming |first=Mike |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/paramount-re-ups-sacha-baron-cohen-but-his-next-comedy-grimsby-moves-to-sony/ |title=UPDATE: Sacha Baron Cohen Hails Leo's 'Wolf' Hooker Anus Coke-Snorting In Paramount Re-Up, As 'Grimsby' Moves To Sony |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-14 |archive-date=2014-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424134115/http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/paramount-re-ups-sacha-baron-cohen-but-his-next-comedy-grimsby-moves-to-sony/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年1月21日，上映日改至2016年2月26日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/southpaw-release-date-july-31-2015/|title=Southpaw Set for July 31st Release; Sacha Baron Cohen Comedy Pushed to 2016|work=Collider|accessdate=21 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122010224/http://collider.com/southpaw-release-date-july-31-2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，上映日定為2016年3月4日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movie/grimsby-2016 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-11-06 |archive-date=2015-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907023252/http://www.comingsoon.net/movie/grimsby-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

臺灣原定2016年5月13日上映，但在上映前一週徹檔。

== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===
《特務大臨演》獲得了負面居多的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評級37%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_brothers_grimsby/ |title=The Brothers Grimsby (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 22, 2016 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216211834/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_brothers_grimsby |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分44，代表「普遍不佳」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-brothers-grimsby |title=The Brothers Grimsby reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=March 22, 2016 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702130415/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-brothers-grimsby |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得6.2分。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾從A+至F之間給了「B+」的評價<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |author=Anthony D'Alessandro |url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/10-cloverfield-lane-brothers-grimsby-zootopia-weekend-box-office-1201718537/ |title=‘Zootopia’ Beats ’10 Cloverfield Lane’ At Box Office, ‘Brothers Grimsby’ Grim |publisher=Deadline |date=2016-03-14 |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613084548/https://deadline.com/2016/03/10-cloverfield-lane-brothers-grimsby-zootopia-weekend-box-office-1201718537/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
美國首週末票房僅330萬，位居當週第八，口碑不佳。首週末成績出爐後，被許多家媒體認為是[[票房炸彈|票房炸彈]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/14/box-office-brothers-grimsby-flopped-because-it-didnt-look-good/#4a36b6f749d7 |title=Box Office: 'Brothers Grimsby' Flopped Because It Looked Like A Bad Movie |publisher=Forbes.com |date= |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206110420/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/14/box-office-brothers-grimsby-flopped-because-it-didnt-look-good/#4a36b6f749d7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

